  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Conduct lessons in accordance with centre curriculum.</li><li>Plan and develop teaching materials.</li><li>Prepare student progress report.</li><li>Assist in centre events and activities.</li><li>Communicate effectively with parents by providing regular updates on students.</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><p><br /></p><ul><li>Minimum Bachelor Degree holder with at least 2 years of relevant working experience</li><li>Good interpersonal and communication skills</li><li>Competence in PC skills (MS Word, Excel, PowerPoint)</li><li>5 days a week (required to work on Saturday & Sunday)</li></ul><p>Chan Wei Wen, Mervyn (Reg. No: R25149588)</p><p>ST Venture EmPloyment Agency (EA License No: 09C5583)</p><p>Please send an updated resume to stvea888@gmail.com if you are keen to apply for this position</p>",
